  "special": {
    "title": "Lyuda",
    "description": "Fires a shot that splits into three horizontal projectiles after a short delay, with the split point determined by time in flight. It also carries an added critical-hit bonus and improved handling."
  },
  "notes": "It is also known as White Death or Lyuda in some versions. In some variants, the extra rounds deal reduced damage compared with the main projectile. The spread briefly collapses after firing but expands again almost immediately, so the effect matters most during sustained fire. Only one Critical Ascensi0n stack can be gained per trigger pull even if multiple projectiles crit. The displayed name varies by platform and patch, with Xbox 360 more likely to show White Death and later releases more commonly using Lyudmila.",
